Privacy Policy
This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Sticker Book (“we" or "us") collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users (each, a "User") of the Sticker Book mobile application.
‍
1. Collection and Use of Information
We may collect and use usage data from Users in the following ways:
‍
1.1. Data Tracking: We utilize Firebase, a mobile and web development platform provided by Google, Inc. ("Firebase"), and Amplitude to track certain information about how Users interact with the App to improve the app and fix bugs. This data is collected and aggregated in a way that does not use any personal information of the Users. The information collected may include, but is not limited to, the User's device type, operating system version, app usage statistics, and geographic location. No private information is collected and no data is sold to any third parties.
‍
1.2. Other Information: In addition we may collect other non-personal information about Users whenever they interact with the App. This information may include technical details such as the User's IP address, browser type, and device identifiers.
‍
2. Data Retention
We retain the collected data for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes outlined in this Privacy Policy or as required by law. Data collected through Firebase and Amplitude may be retained indefinitely for analysis and improvement of our services.
‍
3. Disclosure of Information
We do not sell, trade, or rent Users' personal information to others.
‍
4. Third-Party Integrations
The App integrates with Firebase and Amplitude, which are subject to their own Privacy Policies. By using the App, you acknowledge and agree that Google and Amplitude may process your data in accordance with their privacy practices.
‍
5. Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect the confidentiality, integrity, and availability of the information collected through the App. However, please be aware that no security measures are perfect or impenetrable, and we cannot guarantee the absolute security of your data. No sensitive user data is collected.
‍
6. Changes to this Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. We encourage Users to check this page periodically for any changes. You acknowledge and agree that it is your responsibility to review this Privacy Policy periodically and become aware of modifications.
‍
7. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the practices of the App, please contact us at
stickerbook.ios@gmail.com